Havotron looked away in disgust.  "However, we now know where 
the ship is.  Dreadwind, Darkwing, go."

The two jets blasted off over the cliff skimming along the water 
looking for a dark mass that would be the ship.

Needlenose stepped back, puzzled at where Spinister went.
